k)"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d05u7cu8t000","created":1711675159529,"text":"违约风险This risk is most commonly associated with debt securities."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d05u3ihai400","created":1711674858350,"text":"Business Risk"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d05u8pfsfh40","created":1711675265317,"text":"管理决策失误Business risk is an operating risk, generally caused by poor management decisions."},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d05u3q7tmp40","created":1711674875191,"text":"Prepayment Risk"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d05up8gwro00","created":1711676560570,"text":"when interest rates fall--->借款人把既有的较高利息贷款转移到利息较低的贷款下"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d05u3qfn1ag0","created":1711674875664,"text":"Liquidity Risk"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d05uu3n3x1s0","created":1711676941882,"text":"The risk that an investor might not be able to sell an investment quickly at a fair market price is known as liquidity risk"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d05u3qpjwww0","created":1711674876263,"text":"Regulatory Risk"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d05u3qxcxzk0","created":1711674876735,"text":"Branch topics"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d05u3r63rm80","created":1711674877264,"text":"Branch topics"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d05u3retxoo0","created":1711674877792,"text":"Branch topics"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}